    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the lot? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem, and honestly, it\u2019s in pristine condition. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person! If you want something that\u2019s been truly loved and well-maintained, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
