    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of the S54-powered era. This specimen features the legendary 3.2L atmospheric inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated VANOS system, mated to a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical profile is impeccable: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings were serviced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly health. The limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution across the rear axle, while the suspension geometry remains within factory tolerances with no bushing deflection. The exterior retains its factory depth and gloss, reflecting a life spent in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a high-revving icon with zero track fatigue or cosmetic compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
